{
  "panel_1": [
    {
      "id": "b9b0cc7a-5539-4485-9795-cdbd8014780b",
      "text": "# The Forging of the Shield",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "h1"
    },
    {
      "id": "4e52ac72-ae59-4457-8b1f-ee0a80a44764",
      "text": "First of all Vulcan formed a shield, both large and solid,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "6dd0e92e-b790-4679-a4e1-3cc8abd5cf69",
      "text": "adorning it all over with gold and precious materials;",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "e2ea4bad-f8a5-43ea-8e6c-2d769bafc11f",
      "text": "and around it he threw a shining border, triple, glittering;",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "ff0fd93d-2c04-4d32-8a75-78ee6547356f",
      "text": "and from it suspended a shining silver belt.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "38903171-fc3f-46e3-96bd-d7c970c911f6",
      "text": "Five were the folds of the shield itself;",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "5a09b479-392e-436c-8e5e-cb1f89c88f85",
      "text": "but on it he formed many ornaments with cunning skill.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "80cb6832-7408-45e3-93a3-5e419e558934",
      "text": "On it he wrought the earth, and the heaven, and the sea,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "9ad60ccc-5c98-451d-8709-a592bc5b9ca1",
      "text": "the unwearied sun, and the full moon;",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "254cf7f3-4a31-44bb-afc6-006d209ba5dd",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "hr"
    },
    {
      "id": "24cfb6f7-6b01-4182-b075-cab9f3432424",
      "text": "## The Constellations",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "h2"
    },
    {
      "id": "eac61328-5ac5-4eb1-a758-b2ea36f85542",
      "text": "on it also, all the constellations with which the heaven is crowned,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "3d5e3f6d-8f16-4e61-bebd-1b96931b6ab3",
      "text": "- the Pleiades",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "list"
    },
    {
      "id": "84fdf6f1-ce37-4b8d-a7e1-de8e33d98bf8",
      "text": "- the Hyades",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "list"
    },
    {
      "id": "61fbe74e-0942-4297-8ba5-820bd70755f6",
      "text": "- the might of Orion",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "list"
    },
    {
      "id": "fb64f219-1a3f-4bb1-8e9f-0b8c935055f5",
      "text": "- and the Bear",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "list"
    },
    {
      "id": "ad25ee65-296f-4d8c-9c52-8210b1ee5157",
      "text": "which they also call by the appellation of the Wain,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "54cc1193-1c23-44ba-bd5f-f541e24ab634",
      "text": "which there revolves, and watches Orion;",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "8b5eda72-8792-4235-9b06-1f40374a58e7",
      "text": "but it alone is without a share of the baths of the ocean.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    }
  ],
  "panel_2": [
    {
      "id": "c4f7c4ca-7439-449f-9410-8f87d3dd2cf4",
      "text": "# The Two Beautiful Cities",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "h1"
    },
    {
      "id": "2d244106-8584-4a93-ac42-a910b9ff3d4e",
      "text": "On it also he fashioned two beautiful cities of articulate men.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "ff09aa18-eb4f-4927-b68c-864ddab1779c",
      "text": "In the one, indeed, were marriages and feasts;",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "5ce86a07-a792-429d-9b07-d14dd2746573",
      "text": "and they were conducting the brides from their chambers",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "38d656a2-cfa2-490a-8ff9-84a365e0e110",
      "text": "with brilliant torches, and many a bridal song was raised.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "08a35ede-791a-499c-85de-c59de0d6a14d",
      "text": "The young men were beginning a dance in a circle,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "5efbf186-15df-426b-86b4-9f355eb052a4",
      "text": "and among them flutes and lyres gave forth their sounds;",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "99338675-3e88-47a5-8d7c-d6ebb952ebf1",
      "text": "and the women standing, each at her portals, admired.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "02584d25-b730-4faf-9a69-adf2c6bb4a6e",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "hr"
    },
    {
      "id": "d1ff46a6-4e57-4fff-8edf-cbb044e3ab99",
      "text": "## The Forum",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "h2"
    },
    {
      "id": "f9e3a193-c63e-465d-a633-98b5635c2696",
      "text": "But the people were assembled in the forum,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "28af1ea9-79a8-4e5a-bfa1-436f91ec5ee1",
      "text": "for there a strife had arisen,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "9969bc3e-2a74-427b-98e0-62333f79aeca",
      "text": "and two men strove for the ransom-money of a slain man;",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "ee7375d0-d517-4585-86b3-01c0d382ce1e",
      "text": "both wished to find a termination before a judge.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "972d950d-35e1-4a6a-9b42-1a97c58c37c1",
      "text": "> The people shouted to both, supporters on either side;",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "quote"
    },
    {
      "id": "fe7d15ad-4541-40ce-b088-71145bc23e0f",
      "text": "but the elders sat upon polished stones in a sacred circle,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "869a7076-3fff-4778-9b44-09aee77456ee",
      "text": "and held in their hands the staves of the heralds;",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "213f3682-8045-4360-9dc7-e46bbbd596a3",
      "text": "with these then they arose, and adjudged in turn.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "1fcf999a-90de-48e8-ae15-da88f58b144d",
      "text": "But there lay in the midst two talents of gold,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "edb796d1-1864-4c5b-927e-2d491a3f31c7",
      "text": "to give to him who should pronounce a judgment correctly.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    }
  ],
  "panel_3": [
    {
      "id": "b568e570-11eb-4713-8bfb-56d21e109f9f",
      "text": "# The City Besieged",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "h1"
    },
    {
      "id": "1a5ee070-2f9a-4d45-8ac4-530afab9f3da",
      "text": "But around the other beautiful city sat two armies of people,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "d449e7d6-6485-410d-bacf-64c2eb28ed15",
      "text": "glittering in arms; and a plan was agreeable to them,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "9c679575-3c24-4533-a258-e6ea4fed9b20",
      "text": "either to destroy it entirely, or to divide the wealth.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "fcf531e9-9244-461e-8aa9-7d28126187ed",
      "text": "But they did not yet obey, secretly arming for an ambush;",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "0e977e24-d231-4871-8df8-d5b4e09514e0",
      "text": "their beloved wives and young children stood upon the wall.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "79812f8f-74f0-4686-bbec-4266e9628427",
      "text": "But they advanced; and Mars and Pallas Minerva led them,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "a755d43f-3362-47c1-bb06-361bc9598c9b",
      "text": "both golden, and clad in garments of gold, beautiful and large.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "75618855-257c-43cf-9b18-b4fad1f008d0",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "hr"
    },
    {
      "id": "617803f0-268f-42ab-88ec-7d3b29dcda46",
      "text": "## The Ambush by the River",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "h2"
    },
    {
      "id": "52a5dd5b-39a5-48c6-a29f-acc8f3b2818a",
      "text": "But when they reached a place fit to lay an ambush, by a river,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "84a1c474-55b0-4476-a533-9552c2516dd5",
      "text": "where was a watering-place, they settled in shining brass.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "a8decea9-9af3-4bae-bd24-1b622ef3e523",
      "text": "Two spies watched when they might perceive the sheep and oxen.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "8e1ae93d-91fb-4a9c-8222-72ac5f4cf253",
      "text": "These soon advanced, and two shepherds followed,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "c4060d16-49da-4f12-a40d-e391a081c634",
      "text": "amusing themselves, for they did not foresee the fraud.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "08a33a6d-3ed5-4320-a38e-82f8e7ccd878",
      "text": "The armies ran up, and slaughtered the herds of oxen and sheep.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "7d247ce9-78c6-4a03-b92f-7557b44139a8",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "hr"
    },
    {
      "id": "cdeac3a1-bb27-4351-ad44-6e23d041e7fd",
      "text": "## The Battle",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "h2"
    },
    {
      "id": "a81404d0-0200-4305-9440-71e990124ddd",
      "text": "Then, having formed a line, they fought a battle by the river,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "7cacb254-e562-47d5-8d27-919b4f1ad8b6",
      "text": "and wounded one another with their brazen spears.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "ec057ce6-cb40-47d8-9730-70a2f54bfbb1",
      "text": "Among them mingled Strife and Tumult, and destructive Fate,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "5df60705-3495-4408-ba25-49276ab24a08",
      "text": "and the garment around her shoulders was crimsoned with blood.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    }
  ],
  "panel_4": [
    {
      "id": "9cdd82b8-0842-43b3-ba66-632e9e1fe7bd",
      "text": "# The Fallow Field",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "h1"
    },
    {
      "id": "e692e3fa-7b53-4816-9ab8-b0a13c386923",
      "text": "On it he also placed a soft fallow field, thrice-ploughed;",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "87738f6f-496c-4a5c-8b55-c69a431e4b98",
      "text": "and in it many ploughmen drove hither and thither.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "8ce7e51c-7f05-4e7b-8694-e621e9504922",
      "text": "When they reached the end, a man gave them sweet wine;",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "c426ef8f-a4d1-47d5-9814-f5ebf72e42f5",
      "text": "but it grew black behind, like unto ploughed land,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "bf1d773f-6ec2-481d-9bf9-eeaf71971129",
      "text": "though being of solid gold; which was a very great marvel.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "8fbde38f-c34b-401e-be58-63ab79aa8f12",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "hr"
    },
    {
      "id": "c1f8125d-d579-4f1b-af99-3ce2af90b7a7",
      "text": "## The Harvest",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "h2"
    },
    {
      "id": "28dc1883-3a7b-43ff-b3ce-f32c9941becd",
      "text": "There he also placed a field of deep corn, where reapers worked.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "56cc67bc-3327-4a36-901f-9d80376d0d34",
      "text": "Some handfuls fell thick in series upon the ground,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "1957bcf5-b3cd-49be-ae8f-80ca015acd99",
      "text": "and others the binders of sheaves were tying with straw ropes.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "c293ce96-a8b8-43eb-9d08-69772381761a",
      "text": "And among them the king in silence was standing, rejoicing.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "6062cbcd-6702-4729-a899-258b1fc735ae",
      "text": "Beneath an oak, they had sacrificed a huge ox for the feast.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "a3f45a4d-29ec-472b-88bb-3fb9961c7056",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "hr"
    },
    {
      "id": "a62b3dd4-3cb8-4cf1-aa0a-37189c7a08a7",
      "text": "## The Vineyard",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "h2"
    },
    {
      "id": "88406a77-4217-4aef-be59-c548012b2fb5",
      "text": "On it also he placed a vineyard heavily laden with grapes,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "da14ca74-866b-4510-9a0e-5066682486eb",
      "text": "beautiful, golden; but the clusters throughout were black.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "d73d1a3d-ba2c-4b57-a7ac-e7a1006b20b1",
      "text": "Around it he drew a dark-blue trench, and a hedge of tin.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "7edb6651-390c-4a3f-9091-1ef8bef9967f",
      "text": "Young virgins and youths carried the sweet fruit in baskets.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "2589220e-9413-44fb-a977-cdff5f7f3d01",
      "text": "In the midst of them a boy played pleasantly on a shrill lyre,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "3bb9659b-962a-4ded-9006-e8e15eaff17d",
      "text": "while they followed, beating the ground in a joyful dance.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    }
  ],
  "panel_5": [
    {
      "id": "c2bdbecb-74fd-473d-ac94-e2fc602e6508",
      "text": "# The Herd of Oxen",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "h1"
    },
    {
      "id": "589b0b15-5d80-48ff-a26c-ae95d002f705",
      "text": "On it he also fashioned a herd of lofty-horned oxen;",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "d3972f85-59e1-4594-9da5-c7d1e9f98cfd",
      "text": "but the oxen were made of gold and tin;",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "9bc59141-00bd-40fa-ab00-e12efdf83ad0",
      "text": "and lowing, they rushed from the stall to the pasture,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "7aef02d4-45ae-42c0-afbb-7a53504db2c5",
      "text": "beside a murmuring river, along the waving reed.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "5a499471-958d-41c1-b443-f080ca8b44d0",
      "text": "Four golden herdsmen accompanied them, and nine dogs followed.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "32152636-40fb-4b87-99fd-ce6f1c7038d4",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "hr"
    },
    {
      "id": "9a6943c7-d6a4-43d5-8207-e51e9ce5cdec",
      "text": "## The Lion Attack",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "h2"
    },
    {
      "id": "311bda07-a580-4b73-9c0b-7d06f0c7925d",
      "text": "But two terrible lions among the foremost oxen seized a bull,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "4a0ec782-7a3e-4e65-b902-c47652fc031a",
      "text": "and he, dragging, roared loudly; but the dogs ran up.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "46ca2ebe-5a08-43dd-bf12-32589cba3b6a",
      "text": "The lions indeed, having torn the hide of the huge ox,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "08d32e58-a0b1-41a9-9e2a-c5577d33eb69",
      "text": "were devouring the entrails and the black blood;",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "88940871-17e8-496b-a00d-0f526e539b97",
      "text": "but the shepherds vainly pressed upon them, urging the dogs;",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "083d8c67-bf45-4a64-95a1-ceb5d651b5fb",
      "text": "for they refused to bite the lions, but stood very near, barking.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "af89b364-a5ef-428e-8430-5435f39742a2",
      "text": "On it also the illustrious Vulcan formed a large pasture,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "d9e6492e-bdad-4b02-8f7b-61531e06ca50",
      "text": "a beautiful grove for the white sheep, with covered sheds.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    }
  ],
  "panel_6": [
    {
      "id": "3cf1d80b-1a23-4475-9606-77f146f869c8",
      "text": "# The Dancing Floor",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "h1"
    },
    {
      "id": "62bd212b-0e77-4b2b-9e91-db3de3ab8b38",
      "text": "On it also the illustrious Vulcan embellished a dance,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "e7a7014e-eb46-4be4-ad69-c975d63f54e0",
      "text": "like unto that which in wide Gnossus Daedalus once composed",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "f57aedd7-f337-4f33-a435-91651c362417",
      "text": "for the fair-haired Ariadne.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "6adf21e4-e506-4f1c-8e45-ab8490385366",
      "text": "There the youths and the alluring virgins danced,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "4c010abe-2044-44e0-83d6-207752366ac9",
      "text": "having their hands on each other's wrists.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "87a5214e-d663-4523-a435-a9048e4ad18b",
      "text": "Of these, the virgins had on fine linen robes,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "a8852a7a-f2ea-46f3-adb9-0f4e17aa6bd8",
      "text": "but the youths were dressed in well-woven tunics.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "622cfdcf-dfdf-4a60-becb-bf780bbe7039",
      "text": "These also had beautiful garlands,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "a0ba5f31-995e-45ac-95eb-dd214d476158",
      "text": "and those had golden swords suspended from silver belts.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "168231a1-f182-4fda-a5d9-2eb0c284f084",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "hr"
    },
    {
      "id": "a9f3ac0c-8907-42f7-8f42-53dd9757c71d",
      "text": "## The Performers",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "h2"
    },
    {
      "id": "01909634-011e-4e61-a61d-6d91e73df331",
      "text": "At one time they would move very lightly with skilled feet,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "258c3912-c406-4905-ab4e-e4d5eb5ec05b",
      "text": "as when a potter makes trial of a wheel fitted to his hands;",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "0d172e29-897e-4469-994d-58457b6a3c20",
      "text": "and at another time they would move towards each other.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "e1d24907-1068-4bca-a6e6-0de8b0ea6e88",
      "text": "A large crowd stood around the enjoyable dance, delighted.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "bc0cbb3c-aedd-486f-b414-aec75eae63d2",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "hr"
    },
    {
      "id": "54e7e73c-8fc1-4c0f-b81e-cbd812f9aefd",
      "text": "## The Border",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "h2"
    },
    {
      "id": "ecd4a501-c55d-4c74-a55f-3cbfe72d40e2",
      "text": "But in it he placed the vast strength of the river Oceanus,",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "908ced85-3238-445d-b41c-943b7f76eab3",
      "text": "around the extreme border of the well-formed shield.",
      "created": 1777153032623,
      "type": "text"
    }
  ],
  "panel_7": [
    {
      "id": "4c8180f3-a830-4370-974f-16a348df96a1",
      "text": "# The Dance of Daedalus and the Border of Oceanus",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "h1"
    },
    {
      "id": "e57f2f8c-1e8e-4e47-b29f-bce56629525e",
      "text": "On it also the illustrious Vulcan embellished a dance.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "c71a0231-a19e-4587-b9e7-c53a39257528",
      "text": "It was like the dance in wide Gnossus that Daedalus composed for Ariadne.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "80358478-7819-48f3-afbf-3f7b5ee35af9",
      "text": "There youths and alluring virgins danced with hands on each other's wrists.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "5377b8ba-9de3-4f30-9120-0864031d1ef3",
      "text": "The virgins had fine linen robes, and the youths wore well-woven tunics.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "bda28438-42f6-4c68-b6c3-ee3d954669f1",
      "text": "The youths shone slightly with oil and carried golden swords from silver belts.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "6714269a-0f8d-4724-8c42-83ec31a036bf",
      "text": "At one time they moved lightly with skilled feet, like a potter testing a wheel.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "344c79b0-47ac-4827-a6b9-e2051f023e34",
      "text": "At another time they moved in series towards each other.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "6eecf884-019c-42e0-b5bc-7869f2502718",
      "text": "A large crowd stood around the enjoyable dance, delighted.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "7fddcab7-ff59-46b4-82d7-00c8747239ec",
      "text": "Among them two tumblers, beginning their song, spun round in the midst.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "c21e8219-3777-4500-8fe5-298cd993ede4",
      "text": "---",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "hr"
    },
    {
      "id": "0e18a602-4746-4ef5-94c3-237fa402ef5a",
      "text": "In it he placed the vast strength of the river Oceanus.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "30175d2f-7634-454a-9483-570c129a8c0f",
      "text": "Oceanus ran around the extreme border of the well-formed shield.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "e3f70701-ff64-463b-9560-d40e41982c26",
      "text": "The shield closes where it began: circle, silver belt, dance, river, heaven, sea.",
      "created": 1777152910100,
      "type": "text"
    }
  ],
